莎朗·斯通透露制片人告诉她“和联合主演一起睡觉” https://www.nme.com/news/film/sharon-stone-reveals- Producer-who-told-her-to-sleep-with-costar-3600675?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sharon-stone-reveals-叫她和配角睡觉的制片人Alex BerryWed, 13 Mar 2024 16:01:23 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3600675 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莎朗·斯通" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>演员在最近的采访中透露了制片人的身份</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sharon-stone-reveals-producer-who-told-her-to-sleep-with-costar-3600675">莎朗·斯通揭露制片人告诉她“和联合主演一起睡觉”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莎朗·斯通" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sharon-stone">莎朗·斯通</a>透露了一名电影制片人的身份，该制片人让她与联合主演发生性关系。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-movie-11463-305690">电影评论：边境以南</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位<em>《全面回忆》</em>演员最初<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sharon-stone-recalls-being-asked-to-sleep-with-co-star-by-producer-2904968">在她 2021 年的回忆录</a><em>《两次生活的美丽》</em>中分享了这个故事，但没有提及相关人员的名字。</p><p>现在，斯通在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/louis-theroux">路易斯</a>·塞洛克斯的<a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/gb/podcast/the-louis-theroux-podcast/id1725833532?i=1000648838273" target="_blank" rel="noopener">播客</a>上透露，派拉蒙影业前任负责人、 <em>《罗斯玛丽的婴儿》</em>和<em>《教父</em>》等电影的制片人罗伯特·埃文斯建议她应该和 1992 年的<em>《银》</em>联合主演威廉·鲍德温上床，以提高鲍德温的表现。 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3600691" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3600691" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3600691" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Robert-Evans-co-star-Sharon-Stone.jpg" alt="罗伯特·埃文斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Robert-Evans-co-star-Sharon-Stone.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Robert-Evans-co-star-Sharon-Stone-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Robert-Evans-co-star-Sharon-Stone-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Robert-Evans-co-star-Sharon-Stone-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Robert-Evans-co-star-Sharon-Stone-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Robert-Evans-co-star-Sharon-Stone-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3600691" class="wp-caption-text">罗伯特·埃文斯于 2014 年 3 月 20 日在加利福尼亚州好莱坞。图片来源：Getty/摄影：Gregg DeGuire/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>她解释说：“[埃文斯]戴着墨镜在他的办公室里跑来跑去，解释说他和艾娃·加德纳睡过，我应该和比利·鲍德温睡过，因为[这样]他的表现会更好。”</p><p> “如果我能和比利上床，”她解释道，“那么我们就会在银幕上产生化学反应，从而挽救这部电影。真正的问题是我，因为我太紧张了，不像一个真正的女演员，只要操他就能让事情重回正轨。”</p><p>她补充道：“真正的问题是我太吝啬了。” </p><figure id="attachment_3600687" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3600687" style="width: 1586px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3600687" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-2.jpg" alt="威廉·鲍德温" width="1586" height="1007" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-2.jpg 1586w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Stone-co-star-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1586px) 100vw, 1586px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3600687" class="wp-caption-text">威廉·鲍德温于 1993 年 4 月 26 日在美国加利福尼亚州洛杉矶。图片来源：Getty/摄影：Ron Galella/Ron Galella Collection via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>现年 66 岁的斯通批评了与她搭档的<em>银片</em>演员的选角，将他与 1992 年与她一起主演电影<em>《本能》的</em>迈克尔·道格拉斯进行了比较。她说：“他（埃文斯）不听我为这个角色推荐的演员名单。”</p><p>她继续说道：“我不必操迈克尔·道格拉斯。迈克尔可以来上班，知道如何达到这些目标，台词，排练，然后出现。“现在突然之间，我就陷入了‘我必须操别人’的行业。”</p><p>在其他新闻中，斯通上个月透露，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sharon-stone-pitched-barbie-movie-in-90s-but-was-laughed-at-3572518">早在 90 年代就曾推销过一部与芭比娃娃相关的电影</a>，但“被工作室嘲笑了”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sharon-stone-reveals-producer-who-told-her-to-sleep-with-costar-3600675">莎朗·斯通揭露制片人告诉她“和联合主演一起睡觉”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
